 <name>Pirus</name>
 <channel>bartlett.laurent-laville.org</channel>
 <summary>Pirus is the companion of Pirum to delegate the management of your templates.</summary>
 <description>Pirus will help you to select a theme for your PEAR Channel server, when you build it. 
Pirum provides only a basic theme that cannot be customized easily.
 </description>
 <lead>
  <name>Laurent Laville</name>
